    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin escapes all text inside code tags so you don&#8217;t have to worry about converting code to HTML characters (e.g. <code>&gt;</code>&#8216;s to <code>&amp;gt;</code>&#8216;s). The contents of code tags inside posts and comments are run through php&#8217;s htmlspecialchars.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Unzip <code>wp_codeshield.zip</code>. </li>\n<li>Upload <code>wp_codeshield.php</code> to <code>wp-content/plugins</code>.</li>\n<li>Activate in the Plugins menu.</li>\n</ol>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "This plugin makes it easier to post code in the comments and posts by automatically converting text inside code tags to correct html.",
